doc.after: Trichy or Tiruchi Tamil officially Tiruchirappalli Tamil was formerly anglicized as Trichinopoly in English is a city in the Indian state of Tamil Nadu The city serves as administrative headquarters for Tiruchirappalli District The city is located geographically centre of the state It is the fourth most populous city in the state
